
<section id="contact" class="section-secondary">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center"> Your Story </h2>
        <div class="row row-eq-height">
            <div class="col-md-2 ">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-10">
                <div id="send-story-form">

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <h4> An example: </h4>

                        <p>
                            Some stories people write about themselves: Once, upon a time, there was a princess - Livia. She had beautiful, black long hair.
                            Usually, you couldn't just pass by without noticing her. She was doing just fine in her kingdom, waiting for Prince Charming.
                            And while waiting, she was dating some people, just to keep in shape. Nothing serious.
                            She was attending the healing school of the kingdom. She dreamed as a child to help other people. And after 6 long springs...
                        </p>

                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input id="email-box" type="email" value="" name="email" class="form-input-text form-control" placeholder="Email" required="required">
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <textarea id="internalization-story-box" value="" name="internalization" class="form-input-text form-control" rows="10" placeholder="Internalization Exercise" required="required"><%= internalization%></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <textarea id="externalization-story-box" value="" name="externalization" class="form-input-text form-control" rows="20" placeholder="Externalization Exercise" required="required"><%= externalization%></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <div class="send-button bottom-margin">
                        <button type="submit" onclick="ContactInput.sendStory(this)" class="btn  btn-primary">Save Draft</button>
                        <button type="submit" onclick="ContactInput.sendStory(this)" class="btn  btn-primary">Send Story</button>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <hr>

        <div class="row row-eq-height">
            <div class="col-md-2"></div>
            <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-2">
                <div class="form-group">

                    <p> P.S. We don't have an app yet. But, we have big dreams! Follow us on Social Media. We will announce major updates there.
                        We love Medium btw. We will post the story of the day there. Anonymous of course.
                    </p>

                    <ul class="social-network social-circle">

                        <li><a href="https://medium.com/narrafy" class="icoMedium" title="Medium"><i class="fa fa-medium"></i></a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/narrafy" class="icoFacebook" title="Facebook"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://twitter.com/narrafy" class="icoTwitter" title="Twitter"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a></li>

                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>